Name: Frequency of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' compared to total declarations submitted.
Metric: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' out of all 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' followed by 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'.
Metric: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' out of all 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Number of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' in relation to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'.
Metric: Number of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' activities for cases where activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' occurs

Name: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' out of all rejections.
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'", 'metric_condition': '> 0', 'aggregation': 'percentage', 'filter': "activity LIKE 'Declaration REJECTED by %'"}

Name: Frequency of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' per month.
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'", 'metric_condition': '> 0', 'aggregation': 'total', 'group_by': 'month'}

Name: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' that lead to a new submission by the same employee.
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'", 'metric_condition': '> 0', 'aggregation': 'percentage', 'filter': "activity == 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' AND org:resource == org:resource"}

Name: Number of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' with amounts above 100 euros.
Metric: Number of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' activities > 100 where ma is the last value of case:Amount

Name: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' by 'STAFF MEMBER'.
Metric: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' in the process variants involving 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'.
Metric: Frequency of activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' for cases where activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' occurs

Name: Ratio of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' over 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'.
Metric: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' out of all 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' in the first quarter of the year compared to the rest of the year.
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'", 'metric_condition': '> 0', 'aggregation': 'percentage', 'group_by': 'quarter'}

Name: Number of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' that occur after 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'.
Metric: Number of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' activities for cases where activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' occurs

Name: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' in cases where the budget owner and supervisor are the same person.
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'", 'metric_condition': '> 0', 'aggregation': 'percentage', 'filter': "org:role == 'BUDGET OWNER' AND org:role == 'SUPERVISOR'"}

Name: Frequency of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' in relation to total number of activities in the event log.
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'", 'metric_condition': '> 0', 'aggregation': 'percentage', 'filter': "activity LIKE '%'"}

Name: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' followed by 'Request Payment'.
Metric: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' out of all 'Request Payment'

Name: Number of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' in domestic declarations compared to pre-paid travel costs and requests for payment.
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'", 'aggregation': 'total', 'filter': "activity == 'Request Payment' OR activity LIKE '%travel%'"}

Name: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' that are eventually approved after re-submission.
Metric: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' out of all 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
